[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Annex [bold]C[bold]Transport Select Committee[bold]Inquiry into Safety at Level Crossings[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Examples of recently 
[normal]published
[normal] updates 
[normal]about
[normal] level crossings
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Twitter:[bold]You MUST NOT 
[normal]cross or pass a stop line on a level crossing when the red lights show, an alarm is sounding or barriers are being lowered.
[normal]16 August 2013. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Take extra care when driving close to/crossing tram tracks, especially in the wet, and when crossing rails on bend
[normal]s and at junctions. 
[normal]30 July 2013.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]At level crossings with user-operated barriers, you MUST NOT cross when the red light is showing, only cross if the green light is on.
[normal]14 May 2013.
